            "description": "Struck: modal synthesis of a free-free metal bar. Nine modes at measured free-free ratios (Fletcher & Rossing), each an exponentially decaying resonator. Strike position weights the modes by where their node lines fall; strike hardness sets the contact time of a raised-cosine force pulse, which is what actually filters the top modes out of a soft mallet."
